name: The NOsies Bouquet
description: NOsy Flowers belong to a simple game about truth by Portrait XO.  With an extra large nose, it's out to sniff for half-truths from 1/2 human + 1/2 AI-driven stories.  NOsy is learning to say 'no' when it detects a potential lie.  There's a single NOsy flower minted and this is a whole bouquet.
